snippet.title: The Choreographist - Nilobytes - Combat!
snippet.description:
The Choreographist pits one jerk butt hero and one starry eyed goblin against a horde of shambling boogie men. (Get it? They boogie!)

Here be the second "grunt battle". Second in fifty-song Story Mode. A high-speed, music-based combat against an endless parade of creatures. Score be for notes. Score be for kills. Score be for using your abilities to line them all up, knock them down... and Clear the Dance Floor.

Music got given by J-Punch and Dave Moonshine. So, thank them lots for us, okay?

GET THE FULLY-PLAYABLE, INCOMPLETE THANG FREE RIGHT NOW:
https://akuparagames.itch.io/the-choreographist
